message: Wishing you a happy and healthy 2017!
Time to get to work for the people! Here are my first 7 bills I just introduced in the new session of Congress.
Should Obamacare be repealed?  Let me know what you think in the comments!
Check out the 7 bills I introduced on Congress’s opening day!
Late last night, I voted to back Israel.  Let me know if you agree: our strongest ally in the Middle East deserves America's FULL support!
Looking forward to chairing this important watchdog panel!   Government exists to work for the people, not the other way around.
Attacks on police have to end.   That's why I'm cracking down on cop killers with a new bill!
BAN HORSE SLAUGHTER!  Check out the SAFE Act -- the bill I introduced that will stop this barbaric practice!   Learn more here: http://bit.ly/2jIdLG2

Florida is sending 341 National Guardsmen to Washington, D.C. to provide security assistance at inaugural ceremonies this week.  I deeply appreciate their service. Leave a message of thanks in the comments and I'll pass them along to the brave men and women of the Florida Guard!
The Herald-Tribune nails it – why Congress needs to pass my bill to help Florida's orange growers!
Welcome to the Suncoast, Atlanta Braves! Good luck this season!
Great to see so many Floridians in Washington for the inauguration of the 45th president of the oldest democracy in the world!

Today is the start of tax-filing season. Early filing can help prevent tax identity theft, a growing problem.   If you file first, it will be the tax return filed by a potential thief that will be rejected — not yours.
New study says half of students defaulted or failed to pay down loans within 7 years.   Taxpayers on the hook. Let me know what you think.
Let me know if you agree!
LONG OVERDUE:  A freeze on Syrian refugees and a crackdown on sanctuary cities!   Let me know if you agree: Time to protect Americans!

I had a great talk with Peyton Manning, one of the greatest NFL players of all time.   He had some good tips - I'll be using them in family football games!
I was named co-chair of the Animal Protection Caucus - this should be a bipartisan issue important to all of us!   Learn more: https://t.co/C2CRX4RVgz
Judge Gorsuch is a terrific choice!  Let me know if you agree.

It's Super Bowl weekend!  Now that the manatees have made their picks, who do you think will win?

I wrote a bill to ban pay raises for Congress until the federal budget is BALANCED – because with a national debt of nearly $20 trillion and growing, Congress doesn’t deserve a raise.  Like my page to receive exclusive updates!
